      • loadPullFile

        public Config loadPullFile(Path path,
                           Config sysProps,
                           boolean loadGlobalProperties)
                    throws IOException
        Load a single pull file.
        Parameters:
        path - The Path to the pull file to load, full path
        sysProps - A Config used as fallback.
        loadGlobalProperties - if true, will also load at most one *.properties file per directory from the rootDirectory to the pull file Path.
        Returns:
        The loaded Config.
        Throws:
        IOException

      • loadPullFilesRecursively

        public Collection<Config> loadPullFilesRecursively(Path path,
                                                   Config sysProps,
                                                   boolean loadGlobalProperties)
        Find and load all pull files under a base Path recursively.
        Parameters:
        path - base Path where pull files should be found recursively.
        sysProps - A Config used as fallback.
        loadGlobalProperties - if true, will also load at most one *.properties file per directory from the rootDirectory to the pull file Path for each pull file.
        Returns:
        The loaded Configs.
